MONGO ENVIRONMENT
=================

You'll need to set the following environment variables to get the Mongo connection to work:

MONGO_SERVER
MONGO_PORT
MONGO_DATABASE
MONGO_USER
MONGO_PASSWORD

If you'd like to connect to the remote database from your local version, just ask dave.hoover@gmail.com.


